{"tid":2235478,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"培道中學改校規禁黑口罩及「未經批准」書籍文宣 學生斥荒謬：限制思想自由","createTime":"2020-10-08T17:04:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T18:32:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2775adb79703d87a352b55dd42035975bc1b5ad4","tid":2235478,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T17:04:14.000Z","msg":"九龍城培道中學新學年修改校規，加入不准學生攜帶「與課本無關而未經批准之報刊和書籍」、只可戴指定顏色的口罩、未經學校准許不得穿校服參與學校不認可的集會或活動等條文，犯規者最嚴重或開除學籍。有該校學生形容新校規荒謬，變相禁帶課外書及戴黑口罩。<br />\n<br />\n培道中學本土關注組上周二（29日）在社交媒體發文，指同學在全面復課首日收到新手冊，發現往年十年如一的校規今年「靜雞雞」加了不少條文。該校同學稱，部份班主任派發手冊時曾向同學提及增加了相關條文，但校方並未有在全校早會時提及或解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201009/37SRS5XW4VGWJE5VGXPGFZRNQI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201009%2F37SRS5XW4VGWJE5VGXPGFZRNQI%2F&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr883aCWJNbCOh4I0%2FkJBrkU%3D&h=ee498e73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201009%2F37SRS5XW4VGWJE5VGXPGFZRNQI%2F&h=543767e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201009/37SRS5XW4VGWJE5VGXPGFZRNQI/</a>"},{"pid":"b55f5ec170cf536c9a342cb9a786619e9506e589","tid":2235478,"uid":156863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T17:04:43.000Z","msg":"molamola"},{"pid":"535548a7f335d3a851ec6222746549d156c0a411","tid":2235478,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T17:04:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57443ac190f855520ff23b1b8eecae953a74a96d","tid":2235478,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T17:05:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><